(16, 1, '2013-06-14 18:05:49', '2013-06-14 18:05:49', '<strong>New Subscriptions</strong>\r\nFor a <strong>FREE </strong>subscription to <em>The John Marshall Review of Intellectual Property Law</em>, please fill out the form below and a confirmation email will be sent to you shortly thereafter. You will receive an email from us each time a new issue is released.\r\n\r\n<strong>To Update an Existing Subscription</strong>\r\nPlease fill out the form below with the information used during the initial registration, making sure the email address matches exactly the one you provided, and you will receive an email containing a link to update your information.\r\n\r\n<strong>To Unsubscribe</strong>\r\nSorry to see you go, but you can opt out of receiving emails from <em>The John Marshall Review of Intellectual Property Law</em> each time you receive an email from us. Alternatively, you can fill out the form below with the information used during the initial registration, making sure the email address matches exactly the one you provided, and you will receive an email containing a link to “update your preferences.” Following that link will provide you with another link to unsubscribe.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\n\r\nThe RIPL Editorial Staff\r\n\r\n<div class="signup-form-header"><h4 class="bot-mar-0">Subscription Signup Form</h4></div>\r\n<div id="mc_embed_signup">\r\n<form class="validate" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" action="http://jmripl.us5.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=27428bbcf28cd76e5c8cda991&amp;id=9d49db72f9" method="post" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" novalidate="" target="_blank">\r\n<div class="required-text"><span class="asterisk">*</span> indicates required</div>\r\n<div class="mc-field-group"><label for="mce-FNAME">First Name <span class="asterisk">*</span></label>\r\n<input class="required" id="mce-FNAME" type="text" name="FNAME" value="" /></div>\r\n<div class="mc-field-group"><label for="mce-LNAME">Last Name <span class="asterisk">*</span></label>\r\n<i