(137, 1, '2011-04-04 13:48:44', '2011-04-04 18:48:44', 'Hon. Wei-hua Wu''s article, "International Arbitration of Patent Disputes," has been selected for inclusion in the 2011 edition of the <em>Intellectual Property Law Review</em>, an anthology published annually by Thomson Reuters (West).  The article, 10 J. MARSHALL REV. INTELL. PROP. L. 384 (2011), was published in our winter 2010-2011, volume 10, issue 2. The  article was judged as one of the best law review articles related to intellectual property law published within the last year. Congratulations Hon. Wei-hua Wu.', 'Hon. Wei-hua Wu''s Article Selected for Publication in Intellectual Property Law Review', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hon-wei-hua-wus-article-selected-for-publication-in-intellectual-property-law-review', '', '', '2013-08-20 08:41:09', '2013-08-20 13:41:09', '', 0, 'http://test.jmls.edu/riplblog/?p=137', 0, 'post', '', 0),
