(291, 1, '2013-07-11 15:45:43', '2013-07-11 20:45:43', '<a href="http://test.jmls.edu/riplblog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/iplaw-logo.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-289" alt="The John Marshall Law School Center for Intellectual Property Law" src="http://test.jmls.edu/riplblog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/iplaw-logo.png" width="588" height="133" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe intellectual property law program at The John Marshall Law School is one of the oldest and most comprehensive programs in the country. Intellectual property law remains one of the fastest-growing and most exciting fields today. Intellectual property lawyers counsel and represent clients in all areas of science, technology, business, arts, entertainment, sports and international trade.\r\n\r\n<strong>The John Marshall Law School Center for Intellectual Property Law:</strong>\r\n<a href="http://www.jmls.edu/academics/ip/">http://www.jmls.edu/academics/ip/</a>', 'Resources', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-revision-2', '', '', '2013-07-11 15:45:43', '2013-07-11 20:45:43', '', 23, 'http://test.jmls.edu/riplblog/2013/07/11/23-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
