the protests at military funerals case?  If not, the Court may lose respect or credibility with the general public.\r\n', 'Omega: A Preview for the Rest of the Oct. 2010?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '34-revision-31', '', '', '2013-08-20 08:26:50', '2013-08-20 13:26:50', '', 34, 'http://test.jmls.edu/riplblog/2013/08/20/34-revision-31/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
